spec_data.Name: python2-assimulo
spec_data.License: LGPLv3+ and LGPLv2+ and BSD and GPLv3
spec_data.Description:
Assimulo is a Cython/Python based simulation package that allows for simulation
of both ordinary differential equations (ODEs), f(t,y),
and differential algebraic equations (DAEs), f(t,y,yd).
It combines a variety of different solvers written in C, FORTRAN and
Python via a common high-level interface.
